<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Report of Typing Test</title>
  <style>
      body{
          font-family:'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .theme-bg{
        background-color: #892be262 !important;
      }
      h2, h3{
          margin-top: 0;
          color: #fff;
      }
      .text-theme{
          color: blueviolet !important;
      }
      .text-primary{
          color: #288cfd !important;
      }
      .text-orange{
          color: #ffb405 !important;
      }
      .container{
          padding: 1rem;
          border-radius: 10px;
      }
      .card{
          background-color: #fff;
          padding: 0.5rem 1rem 0.5rem;
          border-radius: 10px;
          max-width: 450px;
      }
      .card > h4, h5{
          font-weight: 300;
      }
      .card > span{
          color: #ffb405;
          font-weight: 700;
      }
      .end-note{
          font-weight: 300;
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="theme-bg container">
    <h2>Hey {{email}}! </h2>
    <h3>Hope you had fun at the Test!</h3>
    <h3>Here's your complete report of the Typing Test.</h3>
    <div class="card">
        <span>Report:</span>
        <h4> You Typed with a speed of <span class='text-theme'> {{wpm}}</span> WPM</h4>
        <h4>The Accuracy of your typing was <span class='text-primary'> {{accuracy}}</span>%</h4>
        <h4>You practiced for <span class='text-orange'> Level {{level}}</span> at {{time}}</h4>
        <p>Visit the website to check more levels that challenge you!</p>
    </div>
    <p>That would be all!</p>
    <h4 class="end-note">Thank you for taking the test. Best Luck!</h4>
  </div>
</body>
</html>